-- Romanian Utility Ecoaqua Awaits Bids for Water Upgrades
-- B y   I r i n a   S a v u
-- 2013-01-23T12:42:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-23/romanian-utility-ecoaqua-awaits-bids-for-water-upgrades.html
The Romanian utility  Ecoaqua SA  is
seeking bids to expand and upgrade the water and sewage network
in the southern town of Calarasi under a contract valued at 36.6
million lei ($11 million) to 40 million lei.  Ecoaqua is waiting for bids under the 18-month contract
until March 25, according to a European Union  procurement
statement  published today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Irina Savu in Bucharest at 
 isavu@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  